Class SecurityCashaccountGroupByCurrencyBaseReport

java.lang.Object
grafioschtrader.reports.SecurityCashaccountGroupByCurrencyBaseReport
Direct Known Subclasses:
AccountPositionGroupSummaryReport
public class SecurityCashaccountGroupByCurrencyBaseReport extends Object
It groups the calculated securities. This class supports two different groupings, one groups the securities by currencies. The other groups them by security account and currencies.
Author:
Hugo Graf
